OL,3,CMeet the 85-year-old fighting lung
OL,4,Cdisease through dance
OL,6,FAn octogenarian who suffers from a
OL,7,Flung disease has found exercise
OL,8,Fclasses at a Carlisle community centre
OL,9,Fhave given him a new lease of life.
OL,11,FGlen Adams, 85, struggled to walk the
OL,12,Fshort distance from the disabled
OL,13,Fparking spaces to the Harraby
OL,14,FCommunity Centre entrance, when he
OL,15,Fstarted rehabilitation classes five
OL,16,Fweeks ago.
OL,18,FNow he proudly parks at the back of
OL,19,Fthe car park, and can make the journey
OL,20,Fwithout issue.
