OL,3,CMeet the 85-year-old fighting lung
OL,4,Cdisease through dance
OL,6,FOn his instructors, Glen said: "You've
OL,7,Fgot a lot of confidence because you're
OL,8,Fin the hands of people who know what
OL,9,Fthey're doing."
OL,11,FGlen's GP referred him to the classes.
OL,12,FHe was once a heavy smoker, but quit
OL,13,F20 years ago - not early enough to
OL,14,Fstop the later onset of his lung
OL,15,Fdisease.
